  * Remove old conffile /etc/menu-methods/fvwm via dpkg-maintscript-helper.
  * Removed dpkg-maintscript-helper rm_conffile /etc/X11/fvwm/system.fvwm2rc
    from install/remove scripts used for wheezy->jessie upgrade.
